('9f5214f5-70ed-4110-8fc0-62b01abe8ee9', 'GG', null, 'Collins Glass', false, 'Pour the Galliano liqueur over ice. Fill the remainder of the glass with ginger ale and thats all there is to it. You now have a your very own GG.'),
