('2b0b7ba8-8ada-4742-82af-843a5ed60740', 'Adam', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine all of the ingredients. Shake well. Strain into a cocktail glass.'),
('5c1463ac-31ea-4d95-b85d-fedceb0fcada', 'B-53', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Layer the Kahlua, Sambucca and Grand Marnier into a shot glas in that order. Better than B-52'),
('288e250f-d59a-4995-82fe-b28bb542a551', 'H.D.', null, 'Beer mug', true, 'Mix the whisky and Baileys Cream in a beer-glass (at least 50 cl). Fill the rest of the glass with coffee.'),
('f85410af-a6f8-43ff-851c-557b85d06c93', 'A. J.', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake ingredients with ice, strain into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('1f67955d-00d9-48a4-a277-0849e4f5d05b', 'Karsk', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Put a copper coin in a coffe-cup and fill up with coffee until you no longer see the coin, then add alcohol until you see the coin. Norwegian speciality.'),
('69cc1550-e84b-4934-95ec-c7ab670aad1f', '50/50', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'fill glass with crushed ice. Add vodka. Add a splash of grand-marnier. Fill with o.j.'),
('9615196c-187a-40a2-8b62-b31b143f0226', 'Melya', null, 'Coffee mug', false, 'Brew espresso. In a coffee mug, place 1 teaspoon of unsweetened powdered cocoa, then cover a teaspoon with honey and drizzle it into the cup. Stir while the coffee brews, this is the fun part. The cocoa seems to coat the honey without mixing, so you get a dusty, sticky mass that looks as though it will never mix. Then all at once, presto! It looks like dark chocolate sauce. Pour hot espresso over the honey, stirring to dissolve. Serve with cream.'),
('354fe8df-2201-42dd-930b-0818183f646b', 'Bijou', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Stir in mixing glass with ice and strain'),
('cde0d8a9-2cb0-49c9-a4fa-a79503ecac11', 'Derby', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Pour all ingredients into a mixing glass with ice. Stir. Strain into a cocktail glass. Garnish with a sprig of fresh mint in the drink.'),
('e859521e-537c-4d1d-8aee-968b1f6e429d', 'Zorro', null, 'Coffee Mug', true, 'add all and pour black coffee and add whipped cream on top.'),
('1aa4e6b4-ed86-46d5-9831-0e8378c0c33c', 'Zinger', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Get a shot glass and pour in three shots of the schnapps. Do the same with the Surge Cola. Then down it like Scheetz would.'),
('f4a2ccdd-0ce2-4768-a2f1-637b4a951fd5', 'Casino', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Pour all ingredients into shaker with ice cubes. Shake well. Strain into chilled cocktail glass. Garnish with a lemon twist and a maraschino cherry. Serve without a straw.'),
('84155e47-ed16-4393-ab26-dc0945700d99', 'Apello', null, 'Collins Glass', false, 'Stirr. Grnish with maraschino cherry.'),
('0a7163de-a138-418d-b576-44563df51137', 'Black and Brown', null, 'Beer pilsner', true, 'CAREFULLY to avoid explosive head formation: Pour Beer glass half full of favorite rootbeer and top off with Guinness.'),
('183f5d66-b6bb-4caf-9da0-18f883a8d152', 'Sangria The  Best', null, 'Pitcher', true, 'Mix wine, sugar and fruit, and let sit in the fridge for 18-24 hours. The mixture will have a somewhat syrupy consistency. Before serving stir in brandy and cut the mixture with soda water until it have a thinner, more wine like consistency. Serve from a pitcher in wine glasses.'),
('b33ff1c9-7d3c-4eb5-b0ab-727d3fbf7385', 'Gin and Soda', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Pour the Gin and Soda water into a highball glass almost filled with ice cubes.
Stir well.
Garnish with the lime wedge.'),
('7475f011-2392-4e7f-8139-fbd9613cc51b', 'Shark Attack', null, 'Pitcher', true, 'Mix lemonade and water according to instructions on back of can. If the instructions say to add 4 1/3 cans of water do so. Mix into pitcher. Add 1 1/2 cup of Vodka (Absolut). Mix well. Pour into glass of crushed ice. Excellent!'),
('caf0a102-8978-4691-bd39-56eeac6c66d2', 'Gin And Tonic', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Pour the gin and the tonic water into a highball glass almost filled with ice cubes. Stir well. Garnish with the lime wedge.'),
('b2018196-cfa5-4c30-9c8f-80daca977a74', 'Lord And Lady', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Pour the rum and Tia Maria into an old-fashioned glass almost filled with ice cubes. Stir well.'),
('a39af719-1c73-4e19-9b43-fb4be0608a03', 'Fuzzy Asshole', null, 'Coffee mug', true, 'fill coffe mug half full of coffee. Fill the other half full of Peach Schnapps. Stir and drink while hot.'),
