('43dcfb69-6182-413a-8334-c68dab7b545d', 'Death in the Afternoon', null, 'Margarita glass', true, 'Easy as you like, pour the absinthe into a chilled glass, top with champagne. Must be drunk mid afternoon for the optimum effect.'),
('4106468a-9e8f-474b-85f5-23dee4d5fede', 'Apple Pie with A Crust', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Just mix the two liquids and sprinkle in the cinnamon. Serve either cold or heated.'),
('dda03a61-cccd-42a3-9abc-890d9adaf369', 'Amaretto Stone Sour Alternative', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Shake sour mix, tequila and amaretto with ice. Strain into highball glass. Add a splash of OJ. Garnish with orange slice and a cherry.'),
('7412a890-e7c0-4034-b576-f2ee39e0693e', 'Brandon and Will''s Coke Float', null, 'Beer mug', true, 'Scoop two large scoops of vanilla ice-cream into frosted beer mug. Next, add 2 ounces Maker''s Mark. Then, pour in coke. Gently stir and enjoy.'),
('a1e7ee50-499d-4f78-aa68-2e44a52a765d', 'Ziemes Martini Apfelsaft', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Serve without ice. At least the juice shold have room temperature.'),
('8120e71f-f15f-427d-a035-4740055084ed', 'Bounty Hunter', null, 'Margarita glass', true, 'Add the spirits into a shaker as well as the pineapple juice, strain into a Margarita glass. Top with Prosecco and garnish with Blueberries.'),
('44036a05-2e63-4b9d-8201-c2686e659de4', 'Blue Hurricane', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'If each part is 1/2 oz then use about 2.5 cups of ice.

Blend it all together.
Drink it with a big straw if you have one.'),
('06bc5850-3270-4138-bdcd-3a51fe7dc3b6', 'Thai Iced Tea', null, 'Highball glass', false, 'Combine Thai tea (i.e., the powder), boiling water, and sweetened condensed milk, stir until blended. Pour into 2 tall glasses filled with ice cubes. Garnish with mint leaves. Makes 2 servings.'),
('2c1e466d-f136-47a1-a517-3b49905277a0', 'Nutty Irishman', null, 'Highball Glass', true, 'Serve over ice'),
('20e20031-2fbf-48a1-9bc2-c909565bfca4', 'Long Island Tea', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Combine all ingredients (except cola) and pour over ice in a highball glass. Add the splash of cola for color. Decorate with a slice of lemon and serve.'),
('2fad630d-9fe5-4f7a-a8d2-7046f146e4ba', 'Thai Iced Coffee', null, 'Highball glass', false, 'Prepare a pot of coffee at a good European strength. In the ground coffee, add 2 or 3 freshly ground cardamom pods. Sweeten while hot, then cool quickly. Serve in highball glass over ice, with cream. To get the layered effect, place a spoon atop the coffee and pour the milk carefully into the spoon so that it floats on the top of the coffee.'),
('5c1785ff-457a-461e-a72d-1a9b6d658978', 'Damned if you do', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'Pour into shot glass. Put in mouth. Repeat as deemed necessary.'),
('7b0e10a7-0c28-4a9a-822f-9e0aea008e5b', '110 in the shade', null, 'Beer Glass', true, 'Drop shooter in glass. Fill with beer'),
('ae7114cd-307b-40e1-8571-7196e9d7a460', 'Girl From Ipanema', null, 'Wine Glass', true, 'Add the cachaca, lemon juice and syrup to your boston glass. Add ice and shake until ice cold. Pour into a chilled flute and top-up with Champagne'),
('997b943f-2271-4995-b056-bd8bbb0f5e4b', 'A Gilligan''s Island', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Shaken, not stirred!'),
