('1c71b0b8-f1e0-4d26-b17c-8e822c59a976', 'Long Island Iced Tea', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Mix all contents in a highball glass and sitr gently. Add dash of Coca-Cola for the coloring and garnish with lemon or lime twist.'),
('27521203-40e3-4d6d-8bde-0260d4c4cce5', 'A Night In Old Mandalay', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine the light rum, añejo rum, orange juice, and lemon juice. Shake well. Strain into a highball glass almost filled with ice cubes. Top with the ginger ale. Garnish with the lemon twist.'),
('750f883c-ed97-4d55-91b0-c371fcb6fadf', '3-Mile Long Island Iced Tea', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Fill 14oz glass with ice and alcohol. Fill 2/3 glass with cola and remainder with sweet & sour. Top with dash of bitters and lemon wedge.'),
('e3b63175-3466-4a7e-9389-2817edf83331', 'Lassi - A South Indian Drink', null, 'Highball Glass', false, 'Blend in a blender for 3 seconds. Lassi is one of the easiest things to make, and there are many ways of making it. Basically, it is buttermilk (yoghurt whisked with water), and you can choose almost any consistency that you like, from the thinnest to the thickest. Serve cold.'),
('237ff390-7be0-4744-a539-4cc0cdbf1fa6', 'Radioactive Long Island Iced Tea', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Pour all ingredients over ice in a very tall glass. Sip cautiously.'),
('746b3f10-9ba0-4239-93ea-768fe18fa9fa', 'Kiss me Quick', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'mix in the glass'),
('73c29bd2-b664-4983-a46e-091c3638990a', 'Mango Orange Smoothie', null, 'Highball Glass', false, 'Throw everything into a blender and liquify.'),
('92a607a5-5212-4ea6-8c09-e5b76e6e9fc1', 'New York Sour', null, 'Whiskey sour glass', true, 'Shake blended whiskey, juice of lemon, and powdered sugar with ice and strain into a whiskey sour glass. Float claret on top. Decorate with the half-slice of lemon and the cherry and serve.'),
('65fa8096-f3fd-484a-80d3-625c1ab141d8', 'New York Lemonade', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Serve in a chilled cocktail glass. Lemon and sugar the rim. Stir and Strain.'),
('e1e594d6-496a-4ee2-90d9-8c1267a0ee2c', 'Sol Y Sombra', null, 'Brandy snifter', true, 'Shake ingredients with ice, strain into a brandy snifter, and serve. (The English translation of the name of this drink is "Sun and Shade", and after sampling this drink, you''ll understand why. Thanks, Kirby.)'),
('77fca4a5-0348-4d8f-8b13-055eb37981c3', 'Zimadori Zinger', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Pour Zima in a collins glass over ice and then pour the shot of Midori. Don''t stir. Garnish with a cherry.'),
('caad6e27-0a47-4b9a-abdd-5b8bb8573e59', '9 1/2 Weeks', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Combine all ingredients in glass mixer. Chill and strain into Cocktail glass. Garnish with sliced strawberry.'),
('b242422d-3278-404e-bc1d-fbe8cf0c6237', 'Affair', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Pour schnapps, orange juice, and cranberry juice over ice in a highball glass. Top with club soda and serve.'),
('04d25b02-f2c3-48b8-9268-a90b292ab781', 'Affinity', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'In a mixing glass half-filled with ice cubes, combine all of the ingredients. Stir well. Strain into a cocktail glass.'),
