('eab85d89-5385-40b0-bae4-cad05c05325a', 'Boomerang', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'In a mixing glass half-filled with ice cubes, combine the gin, vermouth, bitters, and maraschino liqueur. Stir well. Strain into a cocktail glass and garnish with the cherry.'),
