('c64a67fc-198e-48db-a87a-89be4d79aa37', 'Buccaneer', null, 'Beer pilsner', true, 'Pour the corona into an 18oz beer glass pour the bacardi limon into the beer stir very gently'),
('bad2e378-2084-41a8-b157-fc277874fb70', 'Orangeade', null, 'Highball glass', false, 'Place some ice cubes in a large tumbler or highball glass, add lemon juice, orange juice, sugar syrup, and stir well. Top up with cold soda water, serve with a drinking straw.'),
