('cdff5828-d51f-4010-9c8d-08e85814f767', 'Quick-sand', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Simply add the orange juice, quite a quick pour in order to mix the sambucca with the orange juice. The juice MUST have fruit pulp!'),
('fc3244ce-cb72-4be2-8f3c-8fd3447b68ca', 'Kurant Tea', null, 'Champagne flute', true, 'Pour Absolut Kurant into a comfortably big tea-cup. Add the not too hot(!) apple tea and, if you like, some sugar. Enjoy!'),
