('e2386539-1c33-447f-97b9-4f28b866f36e', 'Brandy Sour', null, 'Whiskey sour glass', true, 'Shake brandy, juice of lemon, and powdered sugar with ice and strain into a whiskey sour glass. Decorate with the lemon slice, top with the cherry, and serve.'),
