('594be8d3-5324-48fc-a7a0-6bf8c8a86828', 'Havana Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine all of the ingredients. Shake well. Strain into a cocktail glass.'),
