('0b32c466-35f5-4940-b751-217fb0c31d32', 'Lunch Box', null, 'Pint glass', true, 'Fill a pint glass almost full with beer. Then fill the rest with orange juice (careful not to fill it to the top). Then take the shot of Amaretto and drop it in.'),
('0b0d377a-dd85-45d2-ac9e-4436451db61b', 'Planter''s Punch', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Pour all ingredients, except the bitters, into shaker filled with ice. Shake well. Pour into large glass, filled with ice. Add Angostura bitters, "on top". Garnish with cocktail cherry and pineapple.'),
('f0b8abab-5de5-4783-b8fa-3671f56ea139', 'Planter’s Punch', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Squeeze an orange and strain the juice. Put all the ingredients in a shaker filled with ice and shake for at least 12 seconds. Strain into a highball glass and decorate with a pineapple wedge or fruit of your choice.'),
