('ccd9ab44-50b7-45e3-85b0-9ab1fe273082', 'Frisco Sour', null, 'Whiskey sour glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients (except slices of lemon and lime) with ice and strain into a whiskey sour glass. Decorate with the slices of lemon and lime and serve.'),
('31128d91-bd7d-4699-ab11-54d161981d73', 'Fruit Shake', null, 'Highball Glass', false, 'Blend til smooth.'),
('dbe0430e-622d-4856-8e2a-507325337979', 'Turf Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Stir all ingredients (except orange peel) with ice and strain into a cocktail glass. Add the twist of orange peel and serve.'),
('9121a00a-fd43-41b5-b5a9-deea7adc2fa4', 'Tequila Surprise', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'Fill shot glass with Tequila. Add drops of Tobasco sauce.'),
('4eed1538-240d-468d-8433-af804f10478e', 'A Splash of Nash', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Drop shot glass with banana & melon liquers into a 9 oz hi- ball glass containing soda water and cranberry juice. Drink in one shot.'),
('fbf21dcd-1f62-434c-833b-41145052ca2e', 'Jewel Of The Nile', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'In a mixing glass half-filled with ice cubes, combine all of the ingredients. Stir well. Strain into a cocktail glass.'),
('539595f9-46d2-47d8-b327-86a1e4b9992e', 'Figgy Thyme', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'In a lewis bag, crush up some ice like a baller/maniac (@glacioice). Pour your precious ice into a collins glass. In a cocktail shaker, muddle the figs and thyme together. Add honey vodka, lemon juice, and a large ice cube (@glacioice). Shake until well chilled, and strain into glass. Add tonic water and finally 2 dashes of angostura bitters. Garnish with sliced figs and thyme.'),
('d013f781-f4ca-49bd-9685-3b5bd5f47276', 'Tequila Fizz', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients (except ginger ale) with ice and strain into a collins glass over ice cubes. Fill with ginger ale, stir, and serve.'),
('f36b4a45-2a30-4c90-9d26-e2e264525aa7', 'Imperial Fizz', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients (except carbonated water) with ice and strain into a highball glass over two ice cubes. Fill with carbonated water, stir, and serve.'),
('c9800ece-17c0-4008-a2ba-99919baa21f0', 'Alfie Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Combine and shake all ingredients with ice, strain into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('31f316f6-390e-4b12-92b0-f679c52d1358', 'Lady Love Fizz', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients (except carbonated water) with ice and strain into a cocktail glass over two ice cubes. Fill with carbonated water, stir, and serve.'),
('18cf4ffa-dfbd-4888-9919-ebd08ad89a6e', 'Royal Gin Fizz', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients (except carbonated water) with ice and strain into a highball glass over two ice cubes. Fill with carbonated water, stir, and serve.'),
('8ee94848-2ba0-404a-9aeb-c86f30b6e592', 'Ramos Gin Fizz', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Prepare all the ingredients on the counter to be able to work well and quickly, especially the cream and egg white.

Pour all the ingredients into a shaker.

Shake vigorously for 1 minute: cream and egg white must be mixed perfectly, so don''t rush.

Now open the shaker and put some ice and shake for 1-2 minutes. It depends on how long you can resist!

Pour into a highball glass, add a splash of soda and garnish to taste.

Ramos Gin Fizz was once drunk as an invigorating drink or even as a breakfast, try it as an aperitif and after dinner and you will discover a little gem now lost.'),
('9b68d3e6-3301-4196-b1ae-133cf2525abd', 'Sherry Flip', null, 'Nick and Nora Glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients (except nutmeg) with ice and strain into a whiskey sour glass. Sprinkle nutmeg on top and serve.'),
('5ab72abf-2b2d-40fa-b0b9-11d613af8021', 'Royal Flush', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Pour all the ingredients into tumbler over ice. Strain into glass.'),
('1f1724d6-6ea7-4af1-8085-7ed120efa9d8', 'Herbal flame', null, 'Mason jar', true, 'Pour Hot Damn 100 in bottom of a jar or regular glass. Fill the rest of the glass with sweet tea. Stir with spoon, straw, or better yet a cinnamon stick and leave it in.'),
('4ace8d87-3a13-464e-b4f2-89dba9d2e8a3', 'Port Wine Flip', null, 'Whiskey sour glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients (except nutmeg) with ice and strain into a whiskey sour glass. Sprinkle nutmeg on top and serve.'),
('b36f7251-495e-46c8-bb59-05f48f960803', 'Fruit Flip-Flop', null, 'Highball Glass', false, 'Place all ingredients in the blender jar - cover and whiz on medium speed until well blended. Pour in one tall, 2 medium or 3 small glasses and drink up.'),
('8d685176-487c-4d18-9491-a69d2eff5512', '151 Florida Bushwacker', null, 'Beer mug', true, 'Combine all ingredients. Blend until smooth. Garnish with chocolate shavings if desired.'),
('f1fe8973-323b-404a-b4e1-e54777bc5858', 'Lemon Elderflower Spritzer', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Pour all ingredients over ice, stir and enjoy!'),
('0845f3b6-397a-4b2a-9e6a-3eeb6b043426', 'A Furlong Too Late', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Pour the rum and ginger beer into a highball glass almost filled with ice cubes. Stir well. Garnish with the lemon twist.'),
('b029d0e9-2bfa-4a23-ae14-9184164c4602', 'Orgasm', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients with ice, strain into a chilled cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('bebcea79-10ee-434b-a7da-2e7b5386a3f9', 'Negroni', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Stir into glass over ice, garnish and serve.'),
('01716d3b-4d52-48eb-ae44-19a419f6d9ac', 'Stinger', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Pour in a mixing glass with ice, stir and strain into a cocktail glass. May also be served on rocks in a rocks glass.'),
('6f45a8d4-0c21-4737-8ee9-bcb52de1f7ea', '410 Gone', null, 'Collins Glass', true, ''),
('e042ded5-a592-4a50-bc06-369bf1b89fdd', 'Pink Gin', null, 'White wine glass', true, 'Pour the bitters into a wine glass. Swirl the glass to coat the inside with the bitters, shake out the excess. Pour the gin into the glass. Do not add ice.'),
('7b1564f6-131b-4950-ad08-abbf38c6dc02', 'Shot-gun', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'Pour one part Jack Daneils and one part Jim Beam into shot glass then float Wild Turkey on top.'),
('fd8e37ed-7521-40d7-935b-892029cd0246', 'Gin Sour', null, 'Whiskey sour glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine the gin, lemon juice, and sugar. Shake well. Strain into a sour glass and garnish with the orange slice and the cherry.'),
