('ec73139f-ac1f-46f3-abdf-753ee8a5f248', 'Jitterbug', null, 'Cocktail Glass', true, 'Wet glass, dip rim in sugar. Then add Ice. Then add everything else. It''s that simple!'),
('66618a46-b074-4cb0-a9d8-c7c40dbeb046', 'Greyhound', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Add the vodka to a Collins glass filled with ice.
