('c39bde2f-43ba-4c95-82ef-6540e4ccc623', 'Margarita', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Rub the rim of the glass with the lime slice to make the salt stick to it. Take care to moisten only the outer rim and sprinkle the salt on it. The salt should present to the lips of the imbiber and never mix into the cocktail. Shake the other ingredients with ice, then carefully pour into the glass.'),
('a9be9b0f-c0ce-4c9c-b3be-0349ee3fba13', 'Gagliardo', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake well and serve in a cocktail glass. This is a home cocktail of American/Internet Bar del Pozzo, Pavia, Italy.'),
('70c23b31-b19a-4d2a-9413-5c36bfe1d25f', 'The Galah', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Mix together the alcoholic portions and top with Pineapple and Lime juice.'),
('60e77a73-7ff1-44c3-b095-d3196d780449', 'Blue Margarita', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Rub rim of cocktail glass with lime juice. Dip rim in coarse salt. Shake tequila, blue curacao, and lime juice with ice, strain into the salt-rimmed glass, and serve.'),
('70d48ba0-b2df-478d-b91d-0c8d1f24cf19', 'Grasshopper', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Pour ingredients into a cocktail shaker with ice. Shake briskly and then strain into a chilled cocktail glass.'),
('c9ec7db9-e9a8-45d8-9065-74a5a7ab6a75', 'Singapore Sling', null, 'Hurricane glass', true, 'Pour all ingredients into cocktail shaker filled with ice cubes. Shake well. Strain into highball glass. Garnish with pineapple and cocktail cherry.'),
('704a3e49-fed3-4acf-a0b9-c88dab75d5cf', 'Tommy''s Margarita', null, 'Old-Fashioned glass', true, 'Shake and strain into a chilled cocktail glass.'),
('ad2783f7-3f32-46c8-bb1e-e4b179f7d488', 'Smashed Watermelon Margarita', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'In a mason jar muddle the watermelon and 5 mint leaves together into a puree and strain. Next add the grapefruit juice, juice of half a lime and the tequila as well as some ice. Put a lid on the jar and shake. Pour into a glass and add more ice. Garnish with fresh mint and a small slice of watermelon.'),
('3b5baa7c-bd2d-48f4-8bce-65dab5dac5b1', 'Gin Daisy', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine the gin, lemon juice, sugar, and grenadine. Shake well. Pour into an old-fashioned glass and garnish with the cherry and the orange slice.'),
('4bb84f79-6592-4ebb-8cdc-4ef64a09edff', 'Gin Sling', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Dissolve powdered sugar in mixture of water and juice of lemon. Add gin. Pour into an old-fashioned glass over ice cubes and stir. Add the twist of orange peel and serve.'),
('fa540c0a-fc68-4196-a5b5-beac55286355', 'Gin Smash', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Muddle sugar with carbonated water and mint sprigs in an old-fashioned glass. Add gin and 1 ice cube. Stir, add the orange slice and the cherry, and serve.'),
('22639f9e-dac8-4209-acf2-9136e79cdd8b', 'Gin Toddy', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Mix powdered sugar and water in an old-fashioned glass. Add gin and one ice cube. Stir, add the twist of lemon peel, and serve.'),
('e6fa525e-aabb-4255-ad8f-d740ff361426', 'Gin Tonic', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Fill a highball glass with ice, pour the gin, top with tonic water and squeeze a lemon wedge and garnish with a lemon wedge.'),
('2d71f632-372c-4ff7-a4a5-0a3db7be6a5a', 'Gin Lemon', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'For the preparation of the gin lemon you will not need the shaker. Fill the tumbler with ice, pour the gin and lemonade over it. Gently mix and decorate with a slice of lemon. Those who prefer can also add a few mint leaves. Your gin lemon is ready to be served.'),
('09ebbc3f-583a-42d2-a859-7a9c186f63a2', 'Owen''s Grandmother''s Revenge', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Add ingredients and mix in blender.'),
('4b1df2f5-847b-47a4-91a9-d39edae4e584', 'Gin Cooler', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Stir powdered sugar and 2 oz. carbonated water in a collins glass. Fill glass with ice and add gin. Fill with carbonated water and stir. Add the lemon peel and the orange spiral so that the end of the orange spiral dangles over rim of glass.'),
('506bab8a-295e-46c9-ab8d-176a81cdf0c8', 'Gin Squirt', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Stir gin, grenadine, and powdered sugar with ice and strain into a highball glass over ice cubes. Fill with carbonated water and stir. Decorate with the pineapple chunks and the strawberries and serve.'),
('ed1f819f-1deb-45ae-927c-3a6eb9f9d406', 'Gin Rickey', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Half-fill a tall glass with ice. Mix the gin and Grenadine together and pour over the ice. Add the lime or lemon juice and top off with soda water. Decorate the glass with lime and/or lemon slices.'),
('63b67bae-b80f-40f9-920d-07c0348995b5', 'Gin Swizzle', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine the lime juice, sugar, gin, and bitters. Shake well. Almost fill a colling glass with ice cubes. Stir until the glass is frosted. Strain the mixture in the shaker into the glass and add the club soda.'),
('3603a850-c8d4-4e74-a549-6f46c0252533', 'Gin Basil Smash', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Muddle Basil leaves (~ 10) with Suggar Syrup in a shaker. Add Gin an Lemon Juice.
Filter and serve in a tumbler with ice'),
('75b6e156-8370-43c8-83a9-e68dad3bd435', 'Sloe Gin Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Stir all ingredients with ice, strain into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('80f772d1-89a8-4d42-a5f8-78d4957fd28d', 'Pineapple Gingerale Smoothie', null, 'Highball Glass', false, 'Throw everything into a blender and liquify.'),
('5f115e1d-28c4-4f95-8619-1af281b2630d', 'Godmother', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Pour vodka and amaretto into an old-fashioned glass over ice and serve.'),
('568c047b-0a9b-429b-a7ef-a28f443a0389', 'Blue Lagoon', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Pour vodka and curacao over ice in a highball glass. Fill with lemonade, top with the cherry, and serve.'),
('974a57bc-5177-4485-8ff1-56b69565cbdc', 'Golden dream', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake with cracked ice. Strain into glass and serve.'),
('119b2d19-dbfc-462a-9f8b-554acf67b61d', 'Grass Skirt', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine the gin, triple sec, pineapple juice, and grenadine. Shake well. Pour into an old-fashioned glass and garnish with the pineapple slice.'),
('191106e8-c874-48d3-8389-f35633eb4580', 'Halloween Punch', null, 'Punch bowl', true, 'Tip the cherry juice, orange peel, chilli, cinnamon sticks, cloves and ginger into a large saucepan. Simmer for 5 mins, then turn off the heat. Leave to cool, then chill for at least 4 hrs, or up to 2 days – the longer you leave it the more intense the flavours. If serving to young children, take the chilli out after a few hours.

When you’re ready to serve, pour the juice into a jug. Serve in glass bottles or glasses and pop a straw in each. If you''re adding vodka, do so at this stage. Dangle a fangs sweet from each glass.'),
('6e20e4f5-40ce-43d8-855d-38753ef71226', 'Jackhammer', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Serve over ice- Warning,Deadly!'),
('38b8acce-6edc-4192-ab0d-e7cf7c4465fa', 'Bahama Mama', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Add 2 parts club soda or more or less to taste.

Mix it all together and pour over a bunch of ice. Drink with a straw.'),
('a30ffaa2-505f-4912-a564-c56d4eea5eaf', 'Aloha Fruit punch', null, 'Collins Glass', false, 'Add 1/4 cup water to ginger root. Boil 3 minutes. Strain. Add the liquid to the guava, lemon and pineapple juices. Make a syrup of sugar and remaining water. Cool. Combine with juices and pineapple. Chill throroughly.'),
('b006369e-ffad-43ea-b33d-bd0872fb5900', 'Apple Highball', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Add ice in a highball glass. Rub a wedge of fresh lime around rim and place it in the glass. Add a shot of Apple schnapps, a shot of Courvoisier and top up with ginger ale.'),
('c64aa09c-2a6c-4477-b2ca-9319aa8ea587', 'English Highball', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Pour brandy, gin, and sweet vermouth into a highball glass over ice cubes. Fill with carbonated water. Add the twist of lemon peel, stir, and serve. (Ginger ale may be substituted for carbonated water, if preferred.)'),
('a7730698-2f86-4c74-a007-ed720e14c99c', 'Zipperhead', null, 'Whiskey sour glass', true, 'Fill glass with rocks, add straw before putting in liquor. Then add the ingredients in order, trying to keep layered as much as possible (i.e. Chambord on bottom, then Vodka, Then soda on top).'),
('260ca52e-fb6f-4629-ad6d-3ad3aa669bcf', 'Fahrenheit 5000', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'Cover bottom of shot glass with Tabasco Sauce and then fill with half Firewater and half Absolut Peppar.'),
('356cee00-bf40-4921-b95a-57f9fed53068', 'Artillery', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Stir all ingredients with ice, strain into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('c9c4ecd5-19d6-43e7-98a5-1860deb9dc46', 'Bailey''s Dream Shake', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Blend ingredients for 30 seconds. Definitely refreshing for a hot summer''s day !'),
('8b61f5cf-dfea-41a2-9b97-422dac3f1c14', 'Homemade Kahlua', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Dissolve sugar in 2 cups of boiling water and add corn syrup. Dissolve the instant coffee in the remaining water. Pour syrup and coffee in a gallon jug. Let it cool. Add vodka and vanilla when cold. For the best result, let the mixture "mature" for 4-5 weeks.'),
('1d6d9fae-d9ba-4c46-abe6-eda99155b410', 'John Collins', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Pour all ingredients directly into highball glass filled with ice. Stir gently. Garnish. Add a dash of Angostura bitters.'),
('e228358c-0387-4c2c-8d13-9b3490a63628', 'Midnight Mint', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'If available, rim cocktail (Martini) glass with sugar syrup then dip into chocolate flakes or powder. Add ingredients into shaker with ice. Shake well then strain into cocktail glass.'),
('87d60c8a-e9e2-4eab-96d3-228febe162d3', '24k nightmare', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'Add over ice,shake and pour.'),
('b207e0ce-7a24-482c-ab87-b5044169cd0f', 'Apricot Lady', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine the rum, apricot brandy, triple sec, lemon juice, and egg white. Shake well. Strain into an old-fashioned glass almost filled with ice cubes. Garnish with the orange slice.'),
('02b8bb1e-7d6e-423f-aa3b-92a083eff2dd', 'Kool-Aid Slammer', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'Fill half the shot glass with the kool-aid first. Then put a paper towel over the top of the glass and slowly pour in the vodka. If you do it right, you should be able to see that the two liquids are separated, with the vodka on top. Now slam it! The last thing you''ll taste is the kool-aid.'),
('9059d0e1-81ca-470e-a463-587c21dadb08', 'Sunny Holiday Punch', null, 'Punch bowl', false, 'Combine all ingredients in a punch bowl.'),
('ca53e311-c37c-4fbe-961a-b043a9ce7c87', 'Kamikaze', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients together with ice. Strain into glass, garnish and serve.'),
('c4b3ac15-b47e-40cc-9d4b-68929f4a721d', 'Abilene', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Pour all of the ingredients into a highball glass almost filled with ice cubes. Stir well.'),
('a3db2627-8865-414a-af43-93d9d728fe26', 'Thriller', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine all of the ingredients. Shake well. Strain into a cocktail glass.'),
('65ac64f4-107f-4f90-aa8a-84bd37880f6f', 'Corn n Oil', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Cut the half lime in half again. Add the lime, falernum, and bitters to a rocks glass. Muddle. Add the rum. (Aged Barbados rum such as Plantation 5 Year is recommended). Add ice and stir. Float the blackstrap rum on top. Serve with a straw.'),
('dba3d654-97de-4289-8f7f-464cbdd4635f', 'Rusty Nail', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Pour the Scotch and Drambuie into an old-fashioned glass almost filled with ice cubes. Stir well. Garnish with the lemon twist.'),
('1872f7cc-4cd9-461a-bbdd-54526a178af6', 'Tequila Sour', null, 'Whiskey sour glass', true, 'Shake tequila, juice of lemon, and powdered sugar with ice and strain into a whiskey sour glass. Add the half-slice of lemon, top with the cherry, and serve.'),
('17b3693d-cceb-457a-8ec0-6421b4c227f4', 'Rail Splitter', null, 'Highball glass', false, 'Mix sugar syrup with lemon juice in a tall glass. Fill up with ginger ale.'),
('27e08a4e-0744-4391-bd8d-286eecb8d906', 'Mother''s Milk', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'Shake over ice, strain. Serves two.'),
('981275ad-c4da-4017-aefd-530a21d88952', 'Clove Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Stir all ingredients with ice, strain into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('e6c59fdc-47d2-4b5c-b7f4-e5be2fb2128c', 'Alice Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', false, 'Shake well, strain into a large cocktail glass.'),
('3d45bfdd-194c-41fd-bfb9-c6a08a216ddb', 'Poppy Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake ingredients with ice, strain into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('ef5df0da-8ce9-4ee8-9dfe-3be343850f53', 'Alaska Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Stir all ingredients with ice, strain contents into a cocktail glass. Drop in a twist of lemon and serve.'),
('4e95494f-f4a1-46bb-86d4-ce503b110132', 'Tequila Slammer', null, 'Hurricane glass', true, 'Mix carefully to avoid releasing the dissolved CO2.'),
('fa1269d0-b59d-40e7-b9e8-107831fb31be', 'Artillery Punch', null, 'Punch bowl', true, 'Combine all the ingredients in a large punch bowl with a block of ice. If found too dry, sugar syrup may be added. Decorate with twists of lemon peel.'),
('046dcfb2-9424-481d-a4e5-1a447e4765f8', 'Tequila Sunrise', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Pour the tequila and orange juice into glass over ice. Add the grenadine, which will sink to the bottom. Stir gently to create the sunrise effect. Garnish and serve.'),
('beda30de-8d68-48d1-833f-9241f9f94bea', 'Kill the cold Smoothie', null, 'Highball glass', false, 'Juice ginger and lemon and add it to hot water. You may add cardomom.'),
('139523a1-67dc-46f6-91cb-5771c5c1a2f7', 'Mimosa', null, 'Champagne flute', true, 'Ensure both ingredients are well chilled, then mix into the glass. Serve cold.'),
('c8891195-81d9-41ea-a96d-2411b6496727', 'Grim Reaper', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Mix Kahlua and 151 in glass. Quickly add ice and pour grenadine over ice to give ice red tint.'),
('74a77099-b4c2-45f5-bf49-78b9361a73f7', 'Zima Blaster', null, 'Hurricane glass', true, 'Fill glass with ice. Pour in Chambord, then fill with Zima. Mix and enjoy.'),
('a3391804-41a9-4193-a0ab-bf90fea95ceb', 'Limona Corona', null, 'Beer Glass', true, 'Open the Corona. Fill the empty space in the neck in the bottle with the rum. The bottle should be filled to the top. Plug the bottle with your thumb or the palm of your hand. Turn the bottle upside-down so the rum and beer mix. Turn the bottle rightside-up, unplug, and drink.'),
('73d6d858-175e-4173-ab01-aa46aafd88c7', 'The Jimmy Conway', null, 'Whiskey sour glass', true, 'Fill glass with ice
Pour in The Irishman and Disaronno
Fill to the top with Cranberry Juice
Garnish with a slice of lemon…Enjoy!'),
('5c4d59aa-cc90-4d99-a973-355226a342fb', 'Imperial Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake with ice and strain into cocktail glass.'),
('2a64efa5-94fa-42fd-a523-e70b2158a904', 'Absolut limousine', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Fill Absolut into a glass. Add Lime juice. Add Ice and lime wedges.'),
('43b7bf8e-e27c-44cc-bf51-72ba2c8d4068', 'Absolut Summertime', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Add all ingredients except lemon to shaker filled with ice. Cover and shake vigorously. Strain contents into ice filled collins glass. Garnish with lemon.'),
('c3161c14-2728-491c-8bd5-a3ceabe2b86a', 'Quentin', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine the rum, Kahlua, and cream. Shake well. Strain into a cocktail glass and garnish with the nutmeg.'),
('952a1215-730c-4ff1-a2a0-c3a68200400f', 'Martini', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Straight: Pour all ingredients into mixing glass with ice cubes. Stir well. Strain in chilled martini cocktail glass. Squeeze oil from lemon peel onto the drink, or garnish with olive.'),
('c679cf04-3718-45ca-9a2f-6261cbf67610', 'Zorbatini', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Prepare like a Martini. Garnish with a green olive.'),
('af88a097-46b7-4c60-8a45-4c4c63d61f2e', '747 Drink', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Fill a Collins glass with ice.
Pour in vodka, lime cordial, and cranberry juice.
Fill up with Sprite.
Garnish with a Lime wheel or some cranberries'),
('8220015e-a6dc-4e16-a1e7-5f136d952514', 'Pink Lady', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients with ice, strain into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('b3d702a2-cb41-4fea-bfb4-d7d6f3d7b5f9', 'Gluehwein', null, 'Irish coffee cup', false, 'Boil sugar and spices in water, leave in the water for 30 minutes. Strain the spiced water and mix with the wine. Heat slowly until short of boiling temperature. (To remove alcohol, let it boil for a while.) You may add lemon or orange juice to taste. Serve in irish coffee cup.'),
('4aad4722-83c0-4d2b-950c-f0017d8a79ea', 'Pink Moon', null, 'Whiskey Glass', true, 'Slowly shake in a shaker with ice, strain into a square whiskey glass. Top with fresh ice. Add the blackberries to garnish. Add flowers and a green leaf for a special look!'),
('e1193aba-f13c-4756-b52e-33c4e7f40cfd', 'Mint Julep', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'In a highball glass gently muddle the mint, sugar and water. Fill the glass with cracked ice, add Bourbon and stir well until the glass is well frosted. Garnish with a mint sprig.'),
('eb8a6cba-b02c-4ace-83db-5c2116d27ce8', 'Irish Spring', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Pour all ingredients (except orange slice and cherry) into a collins glass over ice cubes. Garnish with the slice of orange, add the cherry on top, and serve.'),
('0eb88300-9931-4351-aaf4-df195155f0e9', 'Irish Russian', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Add the ingredients in the order listed in the recipe. Care must be taken when adding the Guinness to prevent an excess of foam. Do Not add ice.'),
('a9373972-2904-4969-ab97-7ebbfd014402', 'Frozen Daiquiri', null, 'Champagne flute', true, 'Combine all ingredients (except for the cherry) in an electric blender and blend at a low speed for five seconds, then blend at a high speed until firm. Pour contents into a champagne flute, top with the cherry, and serve.'),
('cab4ff05-ab12-4b15-8af4-f6cdc8eb4114', 'Frozen Mint Daiquiri', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Combine all ingredients with 1 cup of crushed ice in an electric blender. Blend at a low speed for a short length of time. Pour into an old-fashioned glass and serve.'),
('ed53925c-5fb8-41f9-acb3-cd30fae3f534', 'Frozen Pineapple Daiquiri', null, 'Cocktail Glass', true, 'Combine all ingredients with 1 cup of crushed ice in an electric blender. Blend at a low speed for a short length of time. Pour into a cocktail glass and serve.'),
('ac400a30-ba11-492c-b06d-914a9b002c32', 'Vampiro', null, 'Old-Fashioned glass', true, 'Vampiros may be made in a tall glass or an old fashioned glass. Bartenders may first "rim" the glass with Kosher Salt, which is done by placing a layer of Kosher Salt on a chopping board, moistening the glass'' rim with lime juice or water, and then placing the upside down glass rim onto the Kosher Salt, so that the salt sticks to the moistened rim. The second step is to fill half the glass with ice and add one or two shooter glasses full of high quality Tequila. The next stage is to add the flavouring elements. This is done by squeezing a fresh lime into the glass, adding a few grains of salt, adding citrus-flavoured soda pop, until the glass is 4/5 full, and then adding spicy Viuda de Sanchez (or orange juice, lime juice and pico de gallo). The final step is to stir the ingredients so that the flavours are properly blended.'),
('96e773c3-fcca-4a84-a30f-dfdc9f9ec798', 'Kir Royale', null, 'Champagne Flute', true, 'Pour Creme de cassis in glass, gently pour champagne on top'),
('8c419a99-ba7b-43a6-9356-4b8a04270b08', 'Zenmeister', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Mix together and enjoy'),
('62da241d-a328-474f-b5a1-630caa9ad7b3', 'Whisky Mac', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Pour both of the ingredients into a wine goblet with no ice.'),
('7733c48d-cb4e-4e32-8df8-0697dadef218', 'Pisco Sour', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Vigorously shake and strain contents in a cocktail shaker with ice cubes, then pour into glass and garnish with bitters.'),
('2e650ad2-01ea-49dc-ba67-e590e0895245', '3 Wise Men', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'put them them in a glass... and slam it to tha head.'),
('29be224a-7f37-4666-91cb-ef4d58bdd309', 'Adam Sunrise', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Fill blender up with ice. Fill half with Bartons Vodka. Put 10 tsp of sugar, add 1/2 can lemonade concentrate, fill to top with water. Blend for 60 seconds.'),
('eeb81fb9-a694-445d-960c-a2811293f15d', 'Whiskey Sour', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Shake with ice. Strain into chilled glass, garnish and serve. If served ''On the rocks'', strain ingredients into old-fashioned glass filled with ice.'),
('0803573c-337d-4fc5-bf23-6fe3f2d14871', 'Arise My Love', null, 'Champagne flute', true, 'Put creme de menthe into a champagne flute. Fill with chilled champagne and serve.'),
('dca228ed-0921-45e4-b80a-fbea05f2dee6', 'Corpse Reviver', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake, strain, straight up, cocktail glass rinsed with absinthe'),
('6c620b4b-8334-44b6-83ad-d20efcd704fc', 'English Rose Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Rub rim of cocktail glass with lemon juice and dip rim of glass in powdered sugar. Shake all ingredients (except cherry) with ice and strain into sugar-rimmed glass. Top with the cherry and serve.'),
('aba7729c-686f-4c61-9bfa-093bb6775bb9', 'Malibu Twister', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Add rum & trister then, add cranberry jucie,stir'),
('f156cbab-5a55-44a7-8b32-8a187bc84166', 'Arizona Twister', null, 'Hurricane glass', true, 'Just mix in the shots of rum, vodka, and tequila. Add splashes of the three juices, heavy on the pineapple. Top off with grenadine. Crushed ice should already be in glass. Top off the glass with a pineapple wedge.'),
('0bfdc415-7b71-4cd4-80c1-1723d7374b77', 'White Lady', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Add all ingredients into cocktail shaker filled with ice. Shake well and strain into large cocktail glass.'),
('ad8b9bf3-144c-429e-91b3-da0b3031f3e6', 'White Russian', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Pour vodka and coffee liqueur over ice cubes in an old-fashioned glass. Fill with light cream and serve.'),
('65444e0f-1150-4281-9204-cffbce4a7f2b', 'Snake Bite (UK)', null, 'Pint glass', true, 'Pour ingredients into a pint glass. Drink. Fall over.'),
('00804088-74c4-42f0-afb6-7f920bc13902', 'Mojito', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Muddle mint leaves with sugar and lime juice. Add a splash of soda water and fill the glass with cracked ice. Pour the rum and top with soda water. Garnish and serve with straw.'),
('5862212a-69d9-4802-8901-3c03a8413503', 'Mojito Extra', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Put mint with lemon juice in a glas, mash the mint with a spoon, ice, rum & fill up with club soda. Top it with Angostura.'),
('36632bc3-6d70-49c5-821d-7167405f9b36', 'Fruit Cooler', null, 'Highball Glass', false, 'Toss strawberries with sugar, and let sit overnight in refrigerator. Cut lemon, reserve two slices. Juice the rest. Mix together the lemon juice, strawberries, apple juice, and soda water. Add slices of lemon (decor, really). In glasses, put ice cubes, and a slice of apple. Pour drink in, and serve.'),
('c30fd73c-951f-4039-828d-8898995452cd', 'Passion Fruit Martini', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Pour all ingredients into a glass and stir. Garnish with half a passion fruit piece.'),
('d7f40526-cb73-4f28-8013-2c9eaa0cdd13', 'Kiwi Lemon', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Mix in highball glass. Stirr. Garnish with slice of kiwi.'),
('090ff4e2-9749-4a88-949f-e408832c21b0', 'Kiwi Martini', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'The kiwi martini is a very fun vodka cocktail and it is one of the best drinks that makes use of fresh fruit. Though there are a few recipes floating around, this is one of the easiest and it is an absolutely delightful green martini to drink.

For this recipe, you''ll simply muddle slices of kiwi with simple syrup, then shake it with vodka. It''s a drink that anyone can mix up in minutes and a perfect cocktail to show off your favorite vodka.'),
('d062bf2b-6bf7-4e21-af61-34041446dba3', 'Kiwi Papaya Smoothie', null, 'Highball Glass', false, 'Throw everything into a blender and liquify.'),
('80e3f0fe-a70a-42ed-bee1-49c7b62a3649', 'Zizi Coin-coin', null, 'Margarita/Coupette glass', true, 'Pour 5cl of Cointreau on ice, add 2cl of fresh lemon (or lime) juice, stir gently, and finally add slices of lemon/lime in glass.'),
('20c18f7e-a8d8-4560-83e4-bb72b3ed22bd', 'Arizona Stingers', null, 'Hurricane glass', true, 'Place ice cubes in the hurricane glass . Add the 2 HEAPING shots of Absolute Vodka (Note: You can add as many shots of Absolute as you want!) Fill the rest of glass with the Arizona Icetea with lemon. Stir to mix using a spoon. Drink up and enjoy!!!!!!!'),
('b1de6fa3-1c3a-4e84-afc8-8b1747883917', 'Mai Tai', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients with ice. Strain into glass. Garnish and serve with straw.'),
('02df31c6-b1c7-4722-921a-0903fc432d3e', 'Miami Vice', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'First: Mix pina colada with 2.5 oz. of rum with ice(set aside). Second: Mix daiquiri with 2.5 oz. of rum with ice. Third: While frozen, add pina colda mix then daiquiri mix in glass (Making sure they do not get mixed together).'),
('2bd0b0e8-60c6-4928-af7a-198acd4f61c7', 'Lassi Khara', null, 'Highball Glass', false, 'Blend (frappe) in blender until frothy. Add torn curry leaves and serve cold.'),
('07e456d4-9294-4b7a-ab8d-0423a2f36800', 'Lassi Raita', null, 'Highball Glass', false, 'Blend the yoghurt and ice cubes together, until the yoghurt becomes more liquid. Add sugar to taste. The lemon/lime is optional but it gives it a slightly tart taste. Dash of salt. Raita is also good for the summer. Instead of having a traditional salad you can make raita instead.'),
('82823e97-c6ec-45dd-bf60-de21f02654dc', 'Jello shots', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'Boil 3 cups of water then add jello. Mix jello and water until jello is completely disolved. Add the two cups of vodka and mix together. Pour mixture into plastic shot glasses and chill until firm. Then, eat away...'),
('320ba5c3-4d47-40ba-8c5d-c269e1225119', 'Mary Pickford', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake and strain into a chilled large cocktail glass'),
('aee1f5e1-b1b1-468c-a0a1-0bc4cde9cc7e', 'Quarter Deck Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Stir all ingredients with ice, strain into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('c5855843-c9bc-48d8-b6eb-0f176739fe6e', 'Zoksel', null, 'Beer pilsner', true, 'No specific mixinginstructions, just poor every ingredient in one glass. The lemon goes with it.'),
('33c65a10-5d26-4782-a6b9-bce7bea89205', 'Avalon', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Fill a tall glass with ice. Layer the Finlandia Vodka, lemon and apple juices, Pisang Ambon, and top up with lemonade. Stir slightly and garnish with a spiralled cucumber skin and a red cherry. The cucumber provides zest and looks attractive. This drink, created by Timo Haimi, took first prize in the 1991 Finlandia Vodka Long Drink Competition.'),
('2fc08dd2-7e94-43ad-a5c6-da8803ed7359', 'Paloma', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Stir together and serve over ice.'),
('d023bc2e-d061-4df6-b720-9604ed5fb075', 'Bramble', null, 'Old-Fashioned glass', true, 'Fill glass with crushed ice. Build gin, lemon juice and simple syrup over. Stir, and then pour blackberry liqueur over in a circular fashion to create marbling effect. Garnish with two blackberries and lemon slice.'),
('b8e5e318-472b-4ae9-8f21-fcad0fbbe600', 'Almeria', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine all of the ingredients. Shake well. Strain into a cocktail glass.'),
('455343f0-8765-49bd-8e35-8a488ddf0af8', 'Brooklyn', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Combine ingredients with ice and stir until well-chilled. Strain into a chilled cocktail glass.'),
('39a6b489-d27e-42aa-aa40-e24db927c949', 'Snowball', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Place one ice cube in the glass and add 1 1/2 oz of Advocaat. Fill up the glass with lemonade and decorate with a slice of lemon. Serve at once.'),
('c9fafff9-4c69-43ae-8de3-3a752a0b3261', 'Balmoral', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'In a mixing glass half-filled with ice cubes, combine all of the ingredients. Stir well. Strain into a cocktail glass.'),
('54ca0b18-72dd-4817-be5b-dd30c58ef296', '501 Blue', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Mix equal amounts into a glass with ice.'),
('6bf8a02b-3cd9-42f1-8946-aacb8ae371ce', 'The Evil Blue Thing', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Pour ingredients into glass, and drop in a blue whale! The blue whale isn''t really necessary, but it makes the drink more "fun".'),
('e9d62f6c-aa41-4d1a-8130-8eedf5c28138', 'Oatmeal Cookie', null, 'Mason jar', true, 'Just mix it all together.
It''s meant to be a shot, but it works just fine as a proper adult-sized drink over lots of ice.

Tastes like an oatmeal cookie.'),
('ebbb8e19-6992-43e4-8233-48f60ee7201b', 'Cocktail Horse’s Neck', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Wash and brush an organic, untreated lemon, then cut a spiral of lemon peel, using a citrus peel. If it is too large, cut it with a sharp knife.

Put some ice in a tall tumbler glass, place the lemon peel inside and pour the cognac, add the ginger beer and let 2-3 drops of Angostura fall into it. Easy to do, but once you try it you''ll love it.'),
('a15236d8-9109-43bd-975d-91548dc325a9', 'Aperol Spritz', null, 'Wine Glass', true, 'Put a couple of cubes of ice into 2 glasses and add a 50 ml measure of Aperol to each. Divide the prosecco between the glasses and then top up with soda, if you like.'),
('cc7365c2-7b1c-4779-af80-327ab4200939', 'Brave Bull Shooter', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'Pour Tabasco into bottom of shot glass and fill with tequila.'),
('f5767817-5e66-40cd-adcc-17c339c1afb3', 'Blackthorn', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Stir sloe gin and vermouth with ice and strain into a cocktail glass. Add the twist of lemon peel and serve.'),
('185b757e-bf6f-4e95-b292-36bda458dbce', 'Pina Colada', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Mix with crushed ice in blender until smooth. Pour into chilled glass, garnish and serve.'),
('2bc66828-b4a8-4157-8a93-a0d2b6796a23', 'Black Russian', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Pour the ingredients into an old fashioned glass filled with ice cubes. Stir gently.'),
('55a8ed6b-df3d-4a62-b0ad-b4d1fe18b028', 'Apple Slammer', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'pour into a shot glass and present to consumer, they are expected to cover the top of the shotglass with thier palm, raise the glass, slam it on the bar and the swallow quickly.'),
('1ee3878f-139c-4fd6-a6f3-fea50aed04a2', 'The Last Word', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake with ice and strain into a cocktail glass.'),
('ecdba0b7-8c67-4e01-a30c-d87e6a938b99', 'Alabama Slammer', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Pour all ingredients (except for lemon juice) over ice in a highball glass. Stir, add a dash of lemon juice, and serve.'),
('f3eac3ba-ade9-48bb-98da-312045e22380', 'The Laverstoke', null, 'Balloon Glass', true, '1) Squeeze two lime wedges into a balloon glass then add the cordial, Bombay Sapphire and MARTINI Rosso Vermouth, swirl to mix.

2) Fully fill the glass with cubed ice and stir to chill.

3) Top with Fever-Tree Ginger Ale and gently stir again to combine.

4) Garnish with a snapped ginger slice and an awoken mint sprig.'),
('f1fefefc-56e6-4f8c-a707-fc9bc91a6d35', 'Texas Sling', null, 'Wine Glass', true, 'Blend with Ice until smooth. Serve in a tulip glass, top with whip cream.'),
('99426a57-23c9-48fd-8b3b-f7e1851b9f54', 'Tom Collins', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine the gin, lemon juice, and sugar. Shake well. Strain into a collins glass alomst filled with ice cubes. Add the club soda. Stir and garnish with the cherry and the orange slice.'),
('f6b8051a-f09b-48e0-a657-b9f47c252281', 'Slippery Nipple', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'Pour the Sambuca into a shot glass, then pour the Irish Cream on top so that the two liquids do not mix.'),
('7884e2b4-2a34-4afa-adf0-0b7216c26a02', 'Turkeyball', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'Shake with ice and strain into a shot glass.'),
('2fc4dfd2-31da-4bcf-a763-5e08d2c20645', 'Yellow Bird', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake and strain into a chilled cocktail glass'),
('e0dccb0d-78bb-4aa5-8460-d0e78066077a', 'Holloween Punch', null, 'Punch bowl', false, 'Take a bunch of grape juice and a bunch of fizzy stuff (club soda, ginger ale, lemonlime, whatever). Mix them in a punch bowl. Take orange sherbet and lime sherbet. Scoop out scoops and float them in the punch, let them melt a little so that a nasty film spreads all over the top of the punch but there are still "bubbles" in it in the form of sherbet scoops. Looks horrible, tastes just fine.'),
('4f36084c-4161-4d36-972a-c7250862804d', 'Absolut Sex', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Shake Absolut Kurant, Midori, and Cranberry juice in shaker with ice: Strain into rocks glass: Splash of seven on top.Absolut Sex.'),
('3b71aa69-c4bc-4ddf-83c3-017639086769', 'Clover Club', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Dry shake ingredients to emulsify, add ice, shake and served straight up.'),
('688b2bdf-fd99-40bc-82ba-054d63d7a14b', 'Blue Mountain', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine all of the ingredients. Shake well. Strain into an old-fashioned glass almost filled with ice cubes.'),
('216d952b-e4c1-436b-9b67-92e70dd81ecf', 'Rosemary Blue', null, 'Balloon Glass', true, '1) Add the Bombay Sapphire, Blue Curacao, rosemary sprig and gently squeezed lemon wedge to a balloon glass. Swirl well to combine.
2) Fill with cubed ice and top with the Fever-Tree Light Tonic Water.
3) Gently fold with a bar spoon to mix.'),
('16350071-8b36-4631-b733-c8852e0cd389', 'Absolut Evergreen', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Mix, pour over ice and top up with Bitter Lemon.'),
('9aecce0d-e352-4519-bc2b-29030b767333', 'Absolutely Fabulous', null, 'Champagne flute', true, 'Mix the Vodka and Cranberry juice together in a shaker and strain into a glass. Top up with Champagne.'),
('f4182aa9-2866-426d-ad91-555c0cae6213', 'Ipamena', null, 'Wine Glass', false, 'Cut half a lime into pieces, place in a shaker, add the sugar and crush. Measure the passion fruit juice, add it to the shaker and fill up with ice cubes. Close the shaker and shake vigorously. Pour the liquid into a glass, top up with ginger ale, stir with a teaspoon and then garnish the rim of the glass with a slice of lime'),
('717de93e-b4e5-41b3-ab93-175d52eca7f5', 'London Town', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'In a mixing glass half-filled with ice cubes, combine all of the ingredients. Stir well. Strain into a cocktail glass.'),
('0e7a51ab-5115-4a0a-848d-84ad49ec4032', 'Pineapple Paloma', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Rub the rim of each glass with lime slice and dip into salt.
Add ice, tequila, grapefruit juice, lime juice and top with pineapple soda.
Give it a quick stir.
Garnish with fresh pineapple or lime.'),
('aec29065-7383-4ee9-9acd-e28979634896', 'Horse''s Neck', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Pour brandy and ginger ale directly into highball glass with ice cubes. Stir gently. Garnish with lemon zest. If desired, add dashes of Angostura Bitter.'),
('8c870d8f-f2d7-46e2-b095-35dc7f13c229', 'Rum Runner', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Mix all ingredients in glass & add ice.'),
('ea63096c-e1c7-431a-9509-3fdb2023a644', 'Yoghurt Cooler', null, 'Highball Glass', false, 'Place all ingredients in the blender jar - cover and whiz on medium speed until well blended. Pour in one tall, 2 medium or 3 small glasses and drink up. Note: Use lots of ice in this one - great on hot days! To add ice: Remove the center of the cover while the blender is on - drop 3 or 4 ice cubs and blend until they''re completely crushed.'),
('2f2d6fb9-4f72-4268-99dd-0a6fa62a3989', 'Scooter', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients well with cracked ice, strain into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('ac7179b5-7e3b-4757-b910-4f3832e34758', 'Rum Cooler', null, 'Collins glass', true, 'Pour the rum and soda into a collins glass almost filled with ice cubes. Stir well and garnish with the lemon wedge.'),
('871caf46-2783-4323-9f9a-9eb94c5f7e3e', 'Bloody Mary', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Stirring gently, pour all ingredients into highball glass. Garnish.'),
('f3893ae5-c2da-4393-aafd-f61315d20043', 'Wine Cooler', null, 'Collins Glass', false, 'Mix wine and soft drink. Pour into glass. Add ice.'),
('3ce0c3e6-b705-4def-b6b7-a657258f7d22', 'Bloody Maria', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients (except lemon slice) with cracked ice and strain into an old-fashioned glass over ice cubes. Add the slice of lemon and serve.'),
('5105b225-9101-4306-99cf-b3e1ed3605df', 'Hunter''s Moon', null, 'Balloon Glass', true, 'Put the Bombay Sapphire, Martini Bianco, sugar syrup & blackberries in a cocktail shaker with lots of ice and shake vigorously before pouring into a balloon glass, topping up with lemonade and garnishing with a wedge of orange.'),
('09297d52-b618-4bf1-b64b-696a6ad43efd', 'Lemon Drop', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake and strain into a chilled cocktail glass rimmed with sugar.'),
('8872dd13-5a22-4d59-a69a-bf2c65c37b74', 'The Philosopher', null, 'Margarita glass', true, 'Add all the spirits in a shaker (best to use Hendricks gin) as well as the orange bitters and lemon juice. Strain into a Margarita glass, top with Prosecco.'),
('c2cedf61-959c-4332-956f-bc4f015406cf', 'Pornstar Martini', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Straight: Pour all ingredients into mixing glass with ice cubes. Shake well. Strain in chilled martini cocktail glass. Cut passion fruit in half and use as garnish. Pour prosecco into a chilled shot glass and serve alongside the martini.'),
('d869736a-7bdd-4e1b-8a0a-abd3736bf1e2', 'Port Wine Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Stir ingredients with ice, strain into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('33672f00-1781-4028-b43e-886d282becf0', 'Moscow Mule', null, 'Copper Mug', true, 'Combine vodka and ginger beer in a highball glass filled with ice. Add lime juice. Stir gently. Garnish.'),
('ddc4e5fc-a901-4b73-9b99-857d62ebc50f', 'Space Odyssey', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Fill glass with ice and add shots of Bacardi and Malibu. Add splash of pineapple juice and top with orange juice. Add grenadine for color and garnish with cherries.'),
('3a377dc6-7320-471d-a3f8-901d55611102', 'Pure Passion', null, 'Whiskey sour glass', true, 'Mix up all ingredients with a cocktail stirrer and serve with crushed ice with mint and edible flour if available.'),
('21b4ea57-c9a1-4c2f-8b09-66754b2493bd', 'Ice Pick', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Put Vodka in glass fill with iced tea. Stir in lemon to taste.'),
('b16a3d86-d6f3-4fc2-a2c1-3de3f3789fcf', 'Spice 75', null, 'Wine Glass', true, 'Gently warm 60g golden caster sugar in a pan with 30ml water and 1 tbsp allspice. Cook gently until the sugar has dissolved, then leave the mixture to cool. Strain through a sieve lined with a coffee filter (or a double layer of kitchen paper).

Pour 60ml of the spiced syrup into a cocktail shaker along with 200ml rum and 90ml lime juice. Shake with ice and strain between six flute glasses. Top up with 600ml champagne and garnish each with an orange twist.'),
('8b54f918-316e-4afa-9858-b7f1e92fbb09', 'Applejack', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Add all ingredients into mixing glass, chill and strain into cocktail glass'),
('bfc4bc31-77b0-44f8-9780-d3e4a1e1e6f0', 'Apple Karate', null, 'Highball Glass', false, 'Place all ingredients in the blender jar - cover and whiz on medium speed until well blended. Pour in one tall, 2 medium or 3 small glasses and drink up.'),
('dbef5e7a-4fba-46fd-8d47-a6e39b3cc83d', 'Spritz', null, 'Old-Fashioned glass', true, 'Build into glass over ice, garnish and serve.'),
('9a1ad767-e376-4c76-928d-61a35efc3f06', 'Happy Skipper', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Pour Captain Morgan''s Spiced Rum over ice, fill glass to top with Ginger Ale. Garnish with lime. Tastes like a cream soda. Named for the Gilligan''s Island reference ("The Captain" *in* "Ginger" is a Happy Skipper!)'),
('f4067c69-ab91-4804-a638-4902e140f24e', 'Zippy''s Revenge', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Mix Kool-Aid to taste then add Rum and ammaretto. shake well to disolve the sugar in the Kool-Aid... serve cold'),
('10f219c2-a1a3-4407-b8d2-2e9d78424a1f', 'Winter Paloma', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Everyone’s favourite Paloma gets a delicious Indian makeover. Tequila reposado infused with “Timur Pepper” which has citrusy & grapefruit notes and is grown at the foothills of Himalaya. It also produces a slightly numbing and tingling sensation on your lip when consumed. We have also spiced up the fresh grapefruit juice with the warming spice blend from Himalaya. The combination of all these interesting elements has allowed us to elevate your Paloma sipping experience.'),
('1e83d276-9eb3-4a73-8de8-325f4ddecb0f', 'Winter Rita', null, 'Highball Glass', true, 'Salt rim. Combine all ingredients, shake with ice, and strain over fresh ice.⠀'),
('ba2f41fe-c03b-4264-bf42-e70b6c8d65aa', 'Arthur Tompkins', null, 'Whiskey sour glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine the gin, Grand Marnier, and lemon juice. Shake well. Strain into a sour glass and garnish with the lemon twist.'),
('c8d88f13-18e9-44e7-be1b-3787de30fcaa', 'Sazerac', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Rinse a chilled old-fashioned glass with the absinthe, add crushed ice, and set it aside. Stir the remaining ingredients over ice and set it aside. Discard the ice and any excess absinthe from the prepared glass, and strain the drink into the glass. Add the lemon peel for garnish.'),
('5923fcaa-14a6-432b-b5d2-7624f1eae154', 'Rum Sour', null, 'Whiskey sour glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes, combine the rum, lemon juice, and sugar. Shake well. Strain into a sour glass and garnish with the orange slice and the cherry.'),
('3308a2a8-167c-44e8-a034-7264de88f613', 'Brainteaser', null, 'Shot Glass', true, 'layered erin first, then sambuca and then avocart(should sit in middle of other two. To drink: use a straw to suck up avocart then shot the rest and then suck fumes up through straw.'),
('fbd8a554-bcbd-4a3c-bd41-20cee15058ff', 'Lemon Shot', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'Mix Galliano and Absolut Citron in a shot glass, lay lemon wedge sprinkled with sugar over glass and pour a rum over wedge and glass. light rum with a lighter and let burn for a second. Do shot quickly and suck on lemon. If it is done correctly, this will taste like a shot of sweet lemonade.'),
('855f017e-d87d-4fdb-b204-446e01a690d9', 'Stone Sour', null, 'Whiskey sour glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients with ice, strain into a chilled whiskey sour glass, and serve.'),
('fcac4ccf-7acf-4c25-b250-b8a39ad77135', 'Aviation', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Add all ingredients into cocktail shaker filled with ice. Shake well and strain into cocktail glass. Garnish with a cherry.'),
('972f6669-38be-4f2c-8789-a2b49ffce590', 'Tia-Maria', null, 'Collins Glass', true, 'Boil water, sugar and coffe for 10 mins and let cool. Add rum and vanilla. Put in clean bottle(s) and leave for 1 week before using.'),
('1da6ce9f-0e24-4885-a327-24951a30004b', 'Lazy Coconut Paloma', null, 'Highball glass', true, 'Mix the coconut liqueur (preferably tequila) with the grapefruit juice and top with soda water. Garnish with a large grapefruit slice against the inside of the glass.'),
('cf0279e0-0838-4747-a4b3-923198abb5d3', 'Hot Toddy', null, 'Irish coffee cup', true, 'STEP 1
Whisk the whisky and honey together and split between 2 heatproof glasses. Add half of the cinnamon stick to each, then top up with 200ml boiling water.

STEP 2
Add a splash of lemon juice to each, then taste and add more to your preference. Finish each with a slice of lemon, studded with a clove, and serve immediately.'),
('4dab3b74-a96a-43e8-946f-cb2d72de72f7', 'Tipperary', null, 'Nick and Nora Glass', true, 'Stir over ice. Strain into chilled glass. Cut a wide swath of orange peel, and express the orange oils over the drink. Discard orange twist.'),
('df311b24-7bcb-4041-a6c9-8e556af9751d', 'Martinez 2', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Add all ingredients to a mixing glass and fill with ice.

Stir until chilled, and strain into a chilled coupe glass.'),
('1e62ebd7-a0d8-4802-bfbd-73b3e03e1f6e', 'Dry Martini', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Straight: Pour all ingredients into mixing glass with ice cubes. Stir well. Strain in chilled martini cocktail glass. Squeeze oil from lemon peel onto the drink, or garnish with olive.'),
('29c04121-4ac8-4f16-b05c-5fb8e65552ea', 'Martinez Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Stir all ingredients (except cherry) with ice and strain into a cocktail glass. Top with the cherry and serve.'),
('9bf69250-6c14-4d20-838e-099ccd54fd00', 'Kentucky Colonel', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'In a shaker half-filled with ice cubes combine the courbon and Benedictine. Shake and strain into a cocktail glass. Garnish with the lemon twist.'),
('87fca3da-3b21-4b30-a7c3-981da1a34f9a', 'Bruce''s Puce', null, 'Shot glass', true, 'In a regular-sized shot glass, layer, with a spoon or cherry, the grenadine , the Kahlua , then the Bailey''s Irish cream in equal portions. It goes down really smooth ,and you don''t even need a chaser. It tastes just like chocolate milk.(Really!)'),
('d171ceb2-7168-418f-ba6f-555e13d848ba', 'Rum Cobbler', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'In an old-fashioned glass, dissolve the sugar in the club soda. Add crushed ice until the glass is almost full. Add the rum. Stir well. Garnish with the cherry and the orange and lemon slices.'),
('73521def-f42a-40d9-8ab3-892d3c3a7e4c', 'Mountain Bramble', null, 'Old-fashioned glass', true, 'Muddle the blackberries in a tumbler glass. Mix the Gin, lemon juice and sugar syrup in a shaker and strain over chopped ice. Top with Soda water and garnish with more blackberries and some mint'),
('35fc79c3-7e45-48fe-ad39-7ecc86164431', 'Dry Rob Roy', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'In a mixing glass half-filled with ice cubes, combine the Scotch and vermouth. Stir well. Strain into a cocktail glass. Garnish with the lemon twist.'),
('9006f5b5-ae31-46cf-b1d1-1777afcbcf8c', 'Aquamarine', null, 'Martini Glass', true, 'Shake well in a shaker with ice.
Strain in a martini glass.'),
('26b7be0b-4613-4959-9136-4bafa8f6a0bb', 'Adonis Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Stir all ingredients with ice, strain contents into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('ad9601d6-3974-4f26-b67b-7438d07d6790', 'Jack Rose Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients with ice, strain into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('c3eda4e2-d719-4c07-b5bd-be7ecfd21934', 'Zombie', null, 'Hurricane glass', true, 'Blend at high speed for no more than 5 seconds.

Pour into a glass, add ice cubes to fill, then add the garnish.

*Donn’s mix: Bring 3 crushed cinnamon sticks, 1 cup of sugar and 1 cup of water to a boil, stirring until the sugar is dissolved.

Simmer for 2 minutes, then remove from the heat and let sit for at least 2 hours before straining into a clean glass bottle.

Then add 1 part of the syrup and 2 parts of fresh grapefruit juice together.'),
('d2d23cba-6816-4802-975b-295148461efe', 'Quaker''s Cocktail', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake all ingredients with ice, strain into a cocktail glass, and serve.'),
('a1096190-7597-441d-9522-7fb6795563cd', 'Absinthe #2', null, 'Jar', true, 'Mix together and let sit a few days. Strain through a coffee filter. To serve mix 1 part absinthe to 4 parts water, add ice, enjoy.'),
('02d64156-8eee-4499-95f2-fe3c97033940', 'Adam & Eve', null, 'Cocktail glass', true, 'Shake together all the ingredients and strain into a cold glass.');

